People Will Look At You Strange and Say You’ve Changed as If You Worked This Hard To Stay The Same.

I’ve always had an issue with people talking about me and making false narratives about my self, my life and my family. I was always so quick to go into defense mode because I’m an all around good person. I don’t wish bad on anyone & my conscious won’t even allow malicious intent even to people who has wronged me. I say that to say I’ve learned and accepted a new normal. Everyone won’t like me & I will not be able to please them all. I have my family & my circle & their support & love is more than enough. I will never change how I am but definitely who I’m good to. So if you knew me 3 months ago, you really don’t know me at all. This is the Rebirth!! I’m happy & I’m healing & that’s just that. 

It’s so ironic how this trip even came about. After a normal talk with my brother he told me he had plans to go to Singapore and he made it all the way to the airport and just wasn’t feeling it and left. While on the phone he told me he changed it to London and Greece and welcomed me along. I had just told @emims_ & @sinceresaladsandevents that after dropping the kids off I immediately got sad and in my feelings because my kids keep me so busy they tend take my mind away from the pain alot. I told Mario well the kids are gone, so I’ll come. I literally packed and left for a 10 day vacay within 8 hours. It was spare of the moment yet so magical and just what I needed. We stayed at a resort that told us to leave all negativity at the door because the property was built on positivity and love. What are the the odds that he would book us there of all places?? The absolute Best trip hands down!! I didn’t even realize how much I needed it. My mom texted me & said God is Good and I’m so glad you went on this trip. Mane when I say God be doing his thing I mean it. It was meant for Mario not to fly to Singapore because little do he know God needed his help to restore my soul with this vacation. 
Any and everyone who has been there for me, my kids & my businesses during my time out, I can’t thank you enough, I’m forever in debt. #ForeverGrateful

Happy Birthday Reagan Chanel!!
Words can’t explain the love I have for you. My first love, I got it together for you. You changed me, grew me up, taught me responsibilities and priorities. I owe you a lot. I go hard every single day for u & your brother. Thank you for being a good girl…..Respectful, mannerable, studious, intelligent and so kind. You’re so beautiful. You’re everything I prayed for. I got you for life my girl. My little Rich best friend, you can have whatever you like whenever forever. Stay u, stay true, always be a leader & always do the right thing rather someone is watching or not. It’s been such a joy watching you grow & blossom into this amazing almost teenager lol. My Rae, I love you real real bad. We had fun last week & today & more fun is on the way. Surprises all week long because you deserve it. I wish I could gift you the ability to see yourself through my eyes, only then you’ll understand how fucking special you are to me. Happy Birthday Baby Girl; Take 12
